riously and has immediately taken the first steps to investigate. Should any irregularities be proven, the organisation will deal with those involved in an appropriate manner. The NOCs are autonomous organisations, but if any of the cases are confirmed the IOC will not hesitate to impose the strongest sanctions.\"</p><p>The IOC said it will take on board any recommendations from the inquiry to improve the way tickets are allocated and sold internationally.</p>","headline":"IOC to investigate 'black market' Olympic tickets","trailText":"Olympic officials and agents accused of offering tickets in breach of the rules","newspaperPageNumber":"15","shouldHideAdverts":"false","publication":"The Observer","showInRelatedContent":"true","thumbnail":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2012/6/17/1339889823034/The-aquatics-centre-003.jpg","wordcount":"295","commentable":"false","internalContentCode":"391744639","allowUgc":"false","internalOctopusCode":"6310919","isPremoderated":"false","byline":"Cass Jones","newspaperEditionDate":"2012-06-17T00:00:00Z","internalPageCode":"1760857","productionOffice":"UK","liveBloggingNow":"false","commentCloseDate":"2012-06-19T23:38:02Z"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2012/jun/17/black-market-olymipc-tickets-allegations","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/sport/2012/jun/17/black-market-olymipc-tickets-allegations","tags":[{"id":"sport/olympics-2012","webTitle":"Olympic Games 2012","type":"keyword","sectionId":"sport","sectionName":"Sport","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/sport/olympics-2012","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/sport/olympics-2012","references":[]},{"id":"sport/international-olympic-committee","webTitle":"International Olympic Committee","type":"keyword","sectionId":"sport","sectionName":"Sport","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/sport/international-olympic-committee","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/sport/international-olympic-committee","references":